## Share menu

In **WP admin  Voxel  Settings  Share menu,** you can configure the available social networks that you want to be available in the front-end share dialog action.

Available social networks:

- Facebook
- Twitter
- Linkedin
- Reddit
- Tumblr

Messaging apps:

- Telegram
- Whatsapp

Other

- Copy link
- Share via: Triggers the native browser share dialog
